headline: Down More Than 50% From Its High, Is Now a Great Time to Buy Shares of Cava Group?
summary: Mediterranean fast-casual restaurant chain Cava Group (NYSE: CAVA) is a rapidly growing business.  It's often compared to Chipotle Mexican Grill, with investors seeing it as the next big growth stock in the restaurant industry.  Last year was a stellar one for Cava as its shares skyrocketed 162%.
